edu.ucsd.sbrg.sbgn

Class SBGNbuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsd.sbrg.sbgn.SBGNbuilder

  • public class SBGNbuilder
extends Object
    A helper class that facilitates the creation of SBGN map objects. This class wraps an instance of ObjectFactory, which is used to create all the elements. For this reason, the individual methods are not static, because they all rely on one specific ObjectFactory.
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger
